      "The optional memorial 'Saint Jane Frances de Chantal, Religious' has been transferred from Dec. 12 to Aug. 12 since the year 2002 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20000628_guadalupe_lt.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2025.",
      "The optional memorial 'Our Lady of Guadalupe' has been added on December 12th since the year 2008 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20000628_guadalupe_lt.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2025.",
      "The optional memorial 'Saint Juan Diego Cuauhtlatoatzin' has been added on December 9th since the year 2008 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20000628_guadalupe_lt.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2025.",
      "The optional memorial 'Saint John XXIII, Pope' has been added on October 11th since the year 2014 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20140529_decreto-calendario-generale-gxxiii-gpii_en.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2025.",
      "The optional memorial 'Saint John Paul II, Pope' has been added on October 22nd since the year 2014 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20140529_decreto-calendario-generale-gxxiii-gpii_en.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2025.",
      "The optional memorial 'Blessed Virgin Mary of Loreto' has been added on December 10th since the year 2019 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20191007_decreto-celebrazione-verginediloreto_en.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2025.",
