      "The optional memorial 'The Holy Name of the Blessed Virgin Mary' has been added on September 12th since the year 2002 (<a href=\"https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2002/03/22/0150/00449.html\" target=\"_blank\">Vatican Press conference: Presentation of the Editio Typica Tertia of the Roman Missal</a>), applicable to the year 2026.",
