      "The optional memorial 'Saint Paul VI, Pope' has been added on May 29th since the year 2019 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20190125_decreto-celebrazione-paolovi_en.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2026.",
      "The optional memorial 'Saint Faustina Kowalska' has been added on October 5th since the year 2020 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20200518_decreto-celebrazione-santafaustina_en.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2026.",
      "The optional memorial 'Saint Gregory of Narek, Abbot and Doctor of the Church' has been added on February 27th since the year 2021 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20210125_decreto-dottori_en.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2026.",
      "The optional memorial 'Saint John of Avila, Priest and Doctor of the Church', added on May 10th since the year 2021 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20210125_decreto-dottori_en.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), is however superseded by the <i>celebration with precedence over solemnities</i> 'Sixth Sunday of Easter' in the year 2026.",
      "The optional memorial 'Saint Hildegard of Bingen, Virgin and Doctor of the Church' has been added on September 17th since the year 2021 (<a href=\"https://www.vatican.va/roman_curia/congregations/ccdds/documents/rc_con_ccdds_doc_20210125_decreto-dottori_en.html\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2026.",
      "The optional memorial 'Saint Teresa of Calcutta, Virgin' has been added on September 5th since the year 2025 (<a href=\"https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2025/02/11/0125/00250.html#inglese\" target=\"_blank\">Decree of the Dicastery for Divine Worship and the Discipline of the Sacraments</a>), applicable to the year 2026.",
